of the tables and get information of how many Audits Resolutions Reports were published by the CGR each year and by unit audit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Scraping government institution','','inherit','closed','closed','','43-revision-v1','','','2022-10-08 13:53:24','2022-10-08 13:53:24','',43,'http://leoportfolio.local/?p=62',0,'revision','',0);
